sdp/logs/Lead_T-022_20260425T183959Zd_1777178822.log:2348:- `tools/sdp_bridge.py` now follows the task's stored lead agent and `sdp-cli`'s verifier selection defaults instead of forcing a fixed Claude/Codex pair.
